proxmoxbmc (1.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging.
  * All dependencies satisfied by Debian/Proxmox apt packages --
    no pip or venv required.
  * Installs pbmc and pbmcd binaries to /usr/bin/.
